I also like the purple potato cakes.

7
00:02:29,660 --> 00:02:31,140
No, I won't cook them for you.

8
00:02:31,700 --> 00:02:32,300
Why?

9
00:02:36,180 --> 00:02:37,940
His Excellency and Her Highness

10
