14
00:02:43,780 --> 00:02:44,860
It's really admiring!

15
00:02:48,540 --> 00:02:49,860
Just seeing this, they admire us.

16
00:02:50,860 --> 00:02:51,940
Hanging out during the day

17
00:02:52,060 --> 00:02:53,620
is not as free as that in the evening.

18
00:02:55,140 --> 00:02:56,700
