19
00:02:57,100 --> 00:02:58,140
I can take you there.

20
00:02:59,020 --> 00:02:59,700
Where?

21
00:02:59,860 --> 00:03:00,940
Just go with me, then you will know.

22
00:03:08,420 --> 00:03:10,580
You know I'm scared of snakes the most.

23
00:03:11,260 --> 00:03:12,980
Why do you still take me here?

24
00:03:14,580 --> 00:03:15,740
With my company,

25
00:03:16,180 --> 00:03:17,660
they can't hurt you!

26
00:03:18,300 --> 00:03:20,260
You are Aranya here.

27
00:03:21,180 --> 00:03:23,020
It was with their care that you grew up!

28
00:03:23,820 --> 00:03:25,460
Since Aranya was born,

29
00:03:26,420 --> 00:03:27,700
she had been staying there.

30
00:03:29,060 --> 00:03:30,420
Maybe they still know you.

31
00:03:31,260 --> 00:03:33,100
Even if they know me, I dare not go inside.

32
00:03:33,740 --> 00:03:35,660
Why do you take me here?

33
00:03:36,140 --> 00:03:37,140
Do you still remember,

34
00:03:37,460 --> 00:03:38,540
in the Fanyin Valley,

35
00:03:38,980 --> 00:03:40,260
it was through this Python Formation that

36
00:03:40,420 --> 00:03:41,860
we entered the Dream of Aranya by accident?

37
00:03:43,820 --> 00:03:44,580
I'm wondering

38
00:03:46,180 --> 00:03:48,820
if there is something secret in the Python Formation.

39
00:03:53,860 --> 00:03:54,460
Really?

40
00:03:54,980 --> 00:03:56,380
Can we get out?

41
00:03:57,780 --> 00:03:59,900
After all, the Python Formation was made artificially,

42
00:04:00,420 --> 00:04:01,860
which is different from the real one.

43
00:04:02,660 --> 00:04:03,620
After you entered the dream,

44
00:04:03,860 --> 00:04:05,020
I heard

45
00:04:05,460 --> 00:04:06,660
the Dream of Aranya

46
00:04:07,260 --> 00:04:08,580
accidentally drifted to

47
00:04:08,580 --> 00:04:10,340
the Python Formation near the Jieyou Spring.

48
00:04:12,100 --> 00:04:13,820
According to my observation,

49
00:04:13,980 --> 00:04:14,940
the Dream of Aranya

50
00:04:15,060 --> 00:04:16,700
is similar to the Ten-evil Lotus Land,

51
00:04:17,260 --> 00:04:18,700
both of which are magic wards.

52
00:04:19,460 --> 00:04:21,380
Since you could easily

53
00:04:21,500 --> 00:04:23,500
break the Ten-evil Lotus Land to get out,

54
00:04:23,700 --> 00:04:25,980
it may not be difficult to get out
of the Dream of Aranya, either.

55
00:04:26,260 --> 00:04:26,660
Right?

56
00:04:29,300 --> 00:04:30,260
As for this...

57
00:04:31,420 --> 00:04:32,740
Unless you are injured.

58
00:04:36,060 --> 00:04:36,780
So

59
00:04:36,900 --> 00:04:38,820
