60
00:04:40,060 --> 00:04:40,500
Your Majesty.

61
00:04:40,700 --> 00:04:41,700
Tell me the truth.

62
00:04:42,540 --> 00:04:44,540
I don't think

63
00:04:44,620 --> 00:04:46,020
