64
00:04:46,340 --> 00:04:47,940
How did you get injured?

65
00:04:56,340 --> 00:04:58,580
In order to enter the Dream of Aranya with you

66
00:04:58,780 --> 00:05:00,380
without breaking it,

67
00:05:01,220 --> 00:05:03,300
