80
00:05:47,580 --> 00:05:49,780
How could you turn the topic to me again?

81
00:05:52,900 --> 00:05:54,140
The Dream of Aranya

82
00:05:54,540 --> 00:05:56,380
is different from the Ten-evil Lotus Land.

83
00:05:57,060 --> 00:05:57,900
It's much bigger

84
00:05:58,060 --> 00:05:59,060
and more powerful here.

85
00:05:59,660 --> 00:06:01,020
I'm not sure that I can avoid hurting you

86
00:06:01,140 --> 00:06:03,780
while using magic power to break it.

87
00:06:04,380 --> 00:06:05,100
So

88
00:06:06,300 --> 00:06:07,860
let's try to find out

89
00:06:08,420 --> 00:06:09,540
something strange of the Python Formation.

90
00:06:45,100 --> 00:06:45,660
How is it?

91
00:06:45,940 --> 00:06:46,580
How?

92
00:06:52,180 --> 00:06:53,620
If we want to get out of the Python Formation

93
00:06:53,620 --> 00:06:54,740
and the Dream of Aranya,

94
00:06:56,620 --> 00:06:58,340
we have to take the course of Aranya's life

95
00:06:58,340 --> 00:06:59,140
