96
00:07:02,780 --> 00:07:04,180
We can only do this for the time being.

97
00:07:06,700 --> 00:07:07,140
Let's go.

98
00:07:09,580 --> 00:07:11,020
Moye once told me that

99
00:07:11,340 --> 00:07:12,740
he left the Fanyin Valley

100
00:07:12,900 --> 00:07:13,940
after the event of Quanyin Beast happened.

101
00:07:14,100 --> 00:07:15,780
Shen Ye and Aranya stayed in the mansion.

102
00:07:16,140 --> 00:07:17,620
Although they didn't show their heart to each other,

103
00:07:17,740 --> 00:07:19,460
they were deeply attracted to each other

104
00:07:19,620 --> 00:07:20,740
with a sweet life.

105
00:07:21,380 --> 00:07:21,940
Really?

106
00:07:24,620 --> 00:07:25,700
If I have to

107
00:07:25,700 --> 00:07:27,860
take the life course of Aranya,

108
00:07:28,780 --> 00:07:29,900
then I have to...

109
00:07:30,020 --> 00:07:31,340
Naturally, you can't do that.

110
00:07:33,900 --> 00:07:35,180
Then just do as what we said before.

111
00:07:35,500 --> 00:07:37,180
I can keep a distance with Shen Ye.

112
00:07:38,340 --> 00:07:39,820
Moye also told me that

113
00:07:40,300 --> 00:07:43,060
I didn't need to care much about the details.

114
00:07:43,260 --> 00:07:44,780
When I have to make any choices for the big events,

115
00:07:44,900 --> 00:07:46,900
if I do the same as Aranya did, that's OK.

116
00:07:47,740 --> 00:07:49,580
Did Su Moye tell you

117
00:07:49,700 --> 00:07:51,940
what the next big event was?

118
00:07:54,020 --> 00:07:55,020
His Majesty's demise.

119
00:07:55,580 --> 00:07:57,460
It seems to be a long time before that.

120
00:08:00,100 --> 00:08:00,980
Let's go back now.

121
00:08:22,860 --> 00:08:24,860
Having walked for a whole day, I even have blisters on my feet.

122
00:08:25,180 --> 00:08:25,780
Really?

123
00:08:26,980 --> 00:08:28,140
I will give you a foot massage.

124
00:08:34,220 --> 00:08:34,780
What's wrong?

125
00:08:40,340 --> 00:08:40,820
It's nothing.

126
00:08:43,380 --> 00:08:44,180
You can go back first.

127
00:08:44,980 --> 00:08:46,260
What are you going to do?

128
00:08:47,100 --> 00:08:47,700
Don't worry.

129
00:08:48,060 --> 00:08:49,260
I'll be back soon.

130
00:09:16,220 --> 00:09:17,900
