131
00:09:38,540 --> 00:09:40,860
It turned out that you went to take the cotton rose ointment.

132
00:09:41,100 --> 00:09:43,100
Was it necessary for you to behave so secretly?

133
00:09:46,100 --> 00:09:47,660
There isn't cotton rose here.

134
00:09:48,220 --> 00:09:49,980
So I can't make cotton rose ointment.

135
00:09:51,140 --> 00:09:52,100
Then I just took this.

136
00:09:53,580 --> 00:09:54,340
Are you going to

137
00:09:54,380 --> 00:09:55,700
