138
00:10:01,340 --> 00:10:02,580
Why do you think so?

139
00:10:10,220 --> 00:10:10,900
What about this?

140
00:10:11,420 --> 00:10:12,180
How can you explain it?

141
00:10:16,380 --> 00:10:17,580
It's not worth mentioning.

142
00:10:18,380 --> 00:10:19,820
No need to let it disturb you.

143
00:10:20,780 --> 00:10:21,980
It says in the letter that

144
00:10:21,980 --> 00:10:23,340
this is the fifth letter.

145
00:10:24,060 --> 00:10:25,020
No wonder that

146
00:10:25,020 --> 00:10:26,540
I can always smell the flavor of ink.

147
00:10:27,220 --> 00:10:29,020
You have burnt all the letters, right?

148
00:10:30,700 --> 00:10:31,300
It doesn't matter.

149
00:10:32,580 --> 00:10:33,780
I know what to do.

150
00:10:35,940 --> 00:10:37,140
The magic instrument that you asked him to make

151
00:10:37,260 --> 00:10:38,860
has come to the last stage.

152
00:10:39,300 --> 00:10:40,340
As for such masterly magic instrument,

153
00:10:40,460 --> 00:10:42,300
it is the most dangerous when it comes into being.

154
00:10:42,780 --> 00:10:44,140
If it can't be made successfully,

155
00:10:44,380 --> 00:10:46,340
all the efforts will be in vain.

156
00:10:46,420 --> 00:10:47,660
There may also be backfire.

157
00:10:48,100 --> 00:10:50,460
So you'd better go back quickly.

158
00:10:56,100 --> 00:10:57,380
As for Shen Ye...

159
00:10:57,500 --> 00:11:00,300
I know how to behave properly with Shen Ye.

160
00:11:00,700 --> 00:11:01,980
I'm sure to deal with him well.

161
00:11:05,100 --> 00:11:06,500
But I'll be out for a very long time.

162
00:11:06,900 --> 00:11:07,580
Very long?

163
00:11:09,140 --> 00:11:10,340
How long is it?

164
00:11:10,940 --> 00:11:11,740
Several months?

165
00:11:13,940 --> 00:11:14,820
Several years?

166
00:11:17,740 --> 00:11:18,220
Well...

167
00:11:19,940 --> 00:11:21,140
At least several days.

168
00:11:22,660 --> 00:11:23,380
It's just several days.

169
00:11:23,380 --> 00:11:25,220
You said as if you were away for a long time.

170
00:11:28,300 --> 00:11:30,300
Absence sharpens love.

171
00:11:32,460 --> 00:11:33,220
Isn't it long enough?

172
00:11:33,740 --> 00:11:34,380
How could you say that

173
00:11:34,820 --> 00:11:36,300
you were not good at talking?

174
00:11:50,140 --> 00:11:50,740
Your Highness.

175
00:11:50,860 --> 00:11:51,620
Your Excellency.

176
00:11:54,660 --> 00:11:55,420
What's wrong? Chacha.

177
00:11:55,540 --> 00:11:56,140
Tell me!

178
00:11:58,540 --> 00:12:00,100
Here is message from the palace that

179
00:12:00,580 --> 00:12:02,940
His Majesty and Her Majesty haven't seen you for a long time,

180
00:12:03,340 --> 00:12:04,220
so they asked you to go to the palace

181
00:12:04,740 --> 00:12:05,660
to relieve their lovesickness.

182
00:12:16,380 --> 00:12:17,740
I pay respects to father and mother!

183
00:12:18,180 --> 00:12:18,740
Rise!

184
00:12:19,100 --> 00:12:19,700
Thank you, father.

185
00:12:21,460 --> 00:12:22,500
How are you doing these days?

186
00:12:23,220 --> 00:12:25,100
Father, I'm fine.

187
00:12:28,020 --> 00:12:31,940
I heard that Lord Xi Ze had been living
in your mansion these days.

188
00:12:32,500 --> 00:12:35,420
How do you get on with each other?

189
00:12:37,060 --> 00:12:38,300
We get on peacefully

190
00:12:38,420 --> 00:12:40,140
with each other.

191
00:12:41,660 --> 00:12:42,500
It's good.

192
00:12:44,420 --> 00:12:46,700
Just peacefully?

193
00:12:48,580 --> 00:12:50,740
Rumor has it that

194
00:12:51,060 --> 00:12:53,100
Lord Xi Ze and you are closely attached to each other,

195
00:12:53,380 --> 00:12:54,780
which is very admiring.

196
00:12:55,580 --> 00:12:56,540
Mother,

197
00:12:57,140 --> 00:12:58,020
I did go out with Lord Xi Ze

198
00:12:58,180 --> 00:12:59,420
to the fair,

199
00:12:59,740 --> 00:13:01,940
but we didn't do anything that degraded
the decency of the imperial family.

200
00:13:03,340 --> 00:13:03,940
Never mind.

201
00:13:05,420 --> 00:13:07,820
Xi Ze used to be cold.

202
00:13:08,420 --> 00:13:09,860
Since he is kind to you,

203
00:13:10,700 --> 00:13:13,260
we feel very happy for you.

204
00:13:14,420 --> 00:13:16,380
Thank you for caring about me.

205
00:13:18,260 --> 00:13:20,580
If you don't have anything to say, you can leave now.

206
00:13:21,020 --> 00:13:21,420
OK.

207
00:13:23,540 --> 00:13:24,060
By the way,

208
00:13:25,980 --> 00:13:28,060
Shen Ye is making swords in your mansion, isn't he?

209
00:13:28,900 --> 00:13:30,380
How is it going?

210
00:13:31,700 --> 00:13:33,860
Though I don't know much about making swords,

211
00:13:34,460 --> 00:13:35,740
yet I have never heard

212
00:13:35,900 --> 00:13:37,220
he had any worries

213
00:13:37,340 --> 00:13:38,460
or troubles.

214
00:13:38,860 --> 00:13:39,780
So I think

215
00:13:39,820 --> 00:13:41,180
his work goes smoothly.

216
00:13:41,580 --> 00:13:42,980
You think it's smooth?

217
00:13:51,180 --> 00:13:53,940
Such important weapons are being forged in your mansion.

218
00:13:54,740 --> 00:13:57,140
Shouldn't you go to ask something about them?

219
00:13:57,540 --> 00:13:58,660
You're right, mother.

220
00:13:59,260 --> 00:14:01,180
I'm going back to see how it is going.

221
00:14:01,700 --> 00:14:02,380
Well,

222
00:14:03,700 --> 00:14:05,300
I can go back with her

223
00:14:05,620 --> 00:14:07,420
to see how it is going.

224
00:14:09,300 --> 00:14:10,220
Good.

225
00:14:11,020 --> 00:14:13,420
As mother and daughter, you hardly have chances
to talk with each other.

226
00:14:14,220 --> 00:14:14,700
Go ahead.

227
00:14:16,780 --> 00:14:18,220
Then you can have a talk with your father

228
00:14:18,620 --> 00:14:19,220
and wait for me for a while.

229
00:14:19,780 --> 00:14:20,180
I will.

230
00:14:36,580 --> 00:14:38,260
Mother, you know how to make swords, right?

231
00:14:40,180 --> 00:14:40,740
No.

232
00:14:41,900 --> 00:14:43,980
Could it be that you want to take the chance

233
00:14:44,140 --> 00:14:45,940
to talk something with me personally?

234
00:14:51,380 --> 00:14:53,420
Why did Xi Ze have a fancy for you suddenly?

235
00:14:54,820 --> 00:14:56,620
Mother, you are so strange.
How could you ask me such a question?

236
00:14:57,420 --> 00:14:59,100
Lord Xi Ze has been my husband for a long time.

237
00:14:59,700 --> 00:15:00,780
But I heard that

238
00:15:00,860 --> 00:15:03,620
Lord Xi Ze always lived on the Qi Nan Mountain.

239
00:15:04,820 --> 00:15:07,620
Your marriage just existed in the name only.

240
00:15:07,780 --> 00:15:08,300
Mother,

241
00:15:09,300 --> 00:15:10,860
those are just rumors.

242
00:15:11,460 --> 00:15:13,580
Lord Xi Ze and I are always attracted to each other.

243
00:15:14,340 --> 00:15:14,940
Could it be that

244
00:15:15,460 --> 00:15:17,460
you prefer to believe the slanders of the evil people

245
00:15:17,820 --> 00:15:19,340
rather than believe your daughter?

246
00:15:21,300 --> 00:15:22,180
How dare you talk to me like this?

247
00:15:22,940 --> 00:15:23,700
Please calm your anger, mother.

248
00:15:24,060 --> 00:15:25,900
I was just telling the truth.

249
00:15:26,660 --> 00:15:29,380
I'm wondering why you suddenly mentioned Xi Ze.

250
00:15:29,980 --> 00:15:32,540
Could it be that you are worried

251
00:15:33,340 --> 00:15:34,980
after hearing we love each other?

252
00:15:36,620 --> 00:15:38,820
Relying on Xi Ze's favor,

253
00:15:39,940 --> 00:15:41,940
you dare to talk with me like this.

254
00:15:42,820 --> 00:15:43,380
I dare not.

255
00:15:48,260 --> 00:15:49,740
Aranya's mother

256
00:15:50,860 --> 00:15:52,460
really hates her so much.

257
00:16:17,020 --> 00:16:17,460
Mother.

258
00:16:17,820 --> 00:16:19,020
Let me take you to the sword forging room.

259
00:16:19,700 --> 00:16:21,420
No need. I can go there myself.

260
00:16:28,180 --> 00:16:29,780
It's so strange today.

261
00:16:33,820 --> 00:16:36,060
Your Majesty, it's not a long time after your last visit.

262
00:16:37,340 --> 00:16:38,740
Aren't you afraid of His Majesty's suspicion?

263
00:16:40,620 --> 00:16:41,500
Don't worry.

264
00:16:42,100 --> 00:16:43,420
He allowed me to come here.

265
00:16:44,460 --> 00:16:45,740
I don't need to worry about anything.

266
00:16:46,540 --> 00:16:48,220
I'm not the one who is to rebel.

267
00:16:50,420 --> 00:16:51,380
Anyhow,

268
00:16:52,220 --> 00:16:53,860
I won't get you involved in it.

269
00:16:59,900 --> 00:17:02,660
You are not as calm as before.

270
00:17:07,180 --> 00:17:08,540
Today I come here

271
00:17:08,980 --> 00:17:10,500
to ask you again.

272
00:17:11,260 --> 00:17:12,700
If you'd like to join me,

273
00:17:13,340 --> 00:17:14,780
tell me your opinions.

274
00:17:15,860 --> 00:17:17,460
If not,

275
00:17:17,780 --> 00:17:18,820
just tell me directly.

276
00:17:20,300 --> 00:17:21,700
Even without you,

277
00:17:24,220 --> 00:17:25,580
I will still take actions.

278
00:17:45,220 --> 00:17:45,740
Your Highness.

279
00:17:48,300 --> 00:17:49,020
Your Highness.

280
00:17:53,060 --> 00:17:53,660
What's wrong?

281
00:17:53,900 --> 00:17:55,260
The steward said that

282
00:17:55,420 --> 00:17:57,740
Lord Shen Ye invited you to the Mengchun Courtyard.

